snippet.title: ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS – Watchdog Man & Garou DLC Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to PAW-er up for a new round of fighting! Watchdog Man and #Garou are heading to #OnePunchMan: A Hero Nobody Knows as DLC for Character Pack 1 releasing July 21st, 2020! 

Also heading your way is a new stage as part of a free update, later this Summer! Grab your hero gear and follow the link to order your copy today! https://bandainam.co/OnePunchManPO
